iv class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/12/internet-of-things-tutorial-chapter-1-introduction.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next post</strong> <img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/nxt.gif\" width=\"8\"/></a></div>\n<br/>\u00a0<br/>\u00a0\n    <div class=\"addthis_native_toolbox\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tag-data\">Tags: <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/amazon\" rel=\"tag\">Amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/bangalore\" rel=\"tag\">Bangalore</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/big-data\" rel=\"tag\">Big Data</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/fellowship\" rel=\"tag\">Fellowship</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/india\" rel=\"tag\">India</a></div>\n<br/>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">\n     The fellow should be able to lead an independent research program and will be expected to publish high-quality papers during the fellowship period. Apply by Dec 30, 2016.  </p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"post-header-ad\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">kda_sid_write(1); kda_sid_n=2;</script>\n</div>\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/><br/>\n<div class=\"post\" id=\"post-\">\n<img align=\"right\" alt=\"Indian Institute of Science\" height=\"90\" src=\"http://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/opportunities/images/logo-iisc.jpg\" width=\"100\"/>\n<b>At: Indian Institute of Science</b><br/>\n<b>Location: Bangalore, India</b><br/>\n<b>Web: <a href=\"http://www.csa.iisc.ac.in\" target=\"_blank\">www.csa.iisc.ac.in</a></b>\n<br/><br/>\n<br/>\r\nThe Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore is seeking applicants for the inaugural \"<strong>Amazon IISc Young Scientist Big Data Fellowship</strong>\", sponsored by Amazon India and hosted by IISc. This is an 18-month postdoctoral fellowship targeted at outstanding researchers working on:\r\n<br/><br/>\n<ul class=\"three_ul\">\n<li> Foundations of data science, or\r\n<li> Interface between theoretical and practical aspects of machine learning.\r\n</li></li></ul>\r\nThe fellow should be able to lead an independent research program and will be expected to publish high-quality papers during the fellowship period. He/She will be hosted at the Department of Computer Science &amp; Automation at IISc, Bangalore and will have the opportunity to interact with the faculty and graduate students at IISc as well as with researchers at Amazon India. The fellowship offers a handsome stipend with a substantial research grant.\r\n<br/><br/>\n<b>_Contact_:</b><br/>\r\nFor more details and to apply, visit \r\n<br/><a href=\"http://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/opportunities/amazon-fellowship.php\" onclick=\"_gaq.push(['_trackPageview','/x/jobs/16/12-06-iisc._bdf']);\" target=\"_blank\"><b>www.csa.iisc.ac.in/opportunities/amazon-fellowship.php</b></a>\n<br/><br/>\r\nApplication deadline: \r\n<b>December 30, 2016.</b> </div>\n<div class=\"page-link\"></div>\n<div class=\"pagi\">\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/>\n<div class=\"pagi-left\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/12/big-data-main-developments-2016-key-trends-2017.html\" rel=\"prev\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/prv.gif\" width=\"8\"> <strong>Previous post</strong></img></a></div>\n<div class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/12/internet-of-things-tutorial-chapter-1-introduction.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next post</strong> <img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/nxt.gif\" width=\"8\"/></a></div>\n<br/><br/>\n<div>\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/><br/>\n<h2>Top Stories Past 30 Days</h2>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"10\" class=\"latn\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"50%\">\n<table cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"2\">\n<tr><th><b>Most Popular</b></th></tr>\n<tr><td>\n<ol class=\"three_ol\"><li> <a href=\"/2019/04/top-10-coding-mistakes-data-scientists.html\" onclick=\"ga('send','pageview','/x/pbc/2019/04-23-mp-1-mistakes');\"><b>Top 10 Coding Mistakes Made by Data Scientists</b></a>\n<li> <a href=\"/2019/04/recognize-good-data-scientist-job-from-bad.html\" onclick=\"ga('s